
Possible game loop

1) get time
2) if time to run though game loop
	A) update positions
		a) get input, modify user position
			i) if shoot, create bullet object 
		b) loop though list of objects, update position.

	B) check for collisions
		a) if collision bullet
			i) remove enemy object
			ii) add explosion object
			iii) modify score* (if needed)
		b) if collision player
			i)  reduce number of lives
			ii) do a pause or flash warning
				1) if no more lives, exit game loop
				
	C) draw game objects to display buffer
		a) set buffer as ready

